{"type": "article", "id": 5384, "title": "Scrubba 便携洗衣袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-20T07:29:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233818lHLUgtVKW1uaOqP0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t手洗衣物从来都是一项费力又耗时的工作。来自澳大利亚的设计团队 Scrubba 就为出差在外或是旅行露营的人群设计了一款便携洗衣袋，内含微生物和抗水解聚醚 TPU ，可以轻轻松松搞定随身携带衣物，也避免了使用共用洗衣机，远离容器上的病菌，卫生方便。这款便携洗衣袋每次可清洗 5 件衣物，只需清洗 30 秒至 3 分钟，对衣物的损耗程度也与手洗相当，此外还很节水。拎着这件重量不足 145 克的洗衣袋出门，你还会为懒惰找借口吗？定价 54.95 美元（约合人民币 342 元），<a href=\"http://eartheasy.com/the-scrubba-wash-bag\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233815lIPNZLJFaQnWt5Tm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233815o68HVkMltIx2Z05G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233816O983K4VphPb7EQnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233816v75abtJgQ9CfrSUn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233817Y1DQabqMngXF6Cp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}